281
00:29:46,498 --> 00:29:51,435
Y'all go fight now,
we'll watch over your sweethearts,

282
00:29:51,503 --> 00:29:53,767
Hey, Teague,
why ain't you fightin'?

283
00:29:53,839 --> 00:29:56,467
'Cause he's too old,

284
00:29:56,541 --> 00:29:58,805
- Yeah!

286
00:30:01,646 --> 00:30:04,706
